{
  "info": {
    "name": "Restaurant API - Mesas y Reservas",
    "description": "Colección para probar el flujo de mesas, floor-plan, reservas con asignación greedy, gestión del owner e idempotencia. Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1\n\nORDEN RECOMENDADO:\n1) Auth > Register Owner (una vez) y Login Owner\n2) Auth > Register Customer (una vez) y Login Customer\n3) Restaurants > Create Restaurant\n4) Tables > crear M1(2), M2(4), M3(6)\n5) Reservations (customer) > Create Reservation\n6) Reservation management (owner) > ver/seat/complete\n7) Test scenarios > best-fit, conflicto de aforo, dedup doble-click",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Calcula franjas futuras a las 20:00 en días distintos, para que los escenarios",
          "// no compartan mesa entre sí (cada uno reserva en su propio día).",
          "const pad = (n) => String(n).padStart(2, '0');",
          "const slotAt = (daysAhead) => {",
          "  const d = new Date(Date.now() + daysAhead * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);",
          "  return `${d.getFullYear()}-${pad(d.getMonth() + 1)}-${pad(d.getDate())}T20:00`;",
          "};",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('futureSlot', slotAt(30));   // folders 3,4,5",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('slotBestfit', slotAt(31));  // escenario A",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('slotDedup', slotAt(32));    // escenario C"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080/api/v1" },
    { "key": "ownerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ownerUserId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "customerUserId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "restaurantId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tableSmallId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tableMediumId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tableLargeId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "reservationId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "dedupFirstId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "futureSlot", "value": "" },
    { "key": "slotBestfit", "value": "" },
    { "key": "slotDedup", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 - Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Owner + Restaurant (una vez)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('ownerToken', j.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('ownerUserId', j.userId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('restaurantId', j.restaurantId);",
                  "  pm.test('Owner creado con ROLE_OWNER', () => pm.expect(j.restaurantRole).to.eql('OWNER'));",
                  "  pm.test('Devuelve restaurantId', () => pm.expect(j.restaurantId).to.be.a('number'));",
                  "} else {",
                  "  pm.test('Owner ya existía (usa Login Owner + resolver restaurante)', () => pm.expect([400,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"account\": {\n    \"email\": \"owner@test.com\",\n    \"username\": \"owner1\",\n    \"name\": \"Owner Uno\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"tlf\": \"600111222\"\n  },\n  \"restaurant\": {\n    \"name\": \"Restaurante de Pruebas\",\n    \"email\": \"resto-{{$timestamp}}@test.com\",\n    \"tlf\": \"600555666\",\n    \"size\": 12,\n    \"averagePrice\": 25.50,\n    \"cuisineType\": \"SPANISH\",\n    \"dietaryOptions\": [\"VEGETARIAN\", \"GLUTEN_FREE\"],\n    \"street\": \"Calle Mayor 1\",\n    \"city\": \"Madrid\",\n    \"province\": \"Madrid\",\n    \"postalCode\": \"28001\",\n    \"lat\": 40.4168,\n    \"lon\": -3.7038\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register/owner", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "register", "owner"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Owner",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('ownerToken', j.token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('ownerUserId', j.userId);",
                  "pm.test('Token con ROLE_OWNER', () => pm.expect(j.restaurantRole).to.eql('OWNER'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"owner@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Resolver restaurantId del owner (re-runs)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "// Solo necesario tras Login Owner en una sesión nueva (el login no devuelve restaurantId).",
                  "const arr = pm.response.json();",
                  "const ownerId = Number(pm.collectionVariables.get('ownerUserId'));",
                  "const mine = arr.find(r => r.ownerId === ownerId);",
                  "pm.test('Encontrado el restaurante del owner', () => pm.expect(mine).to.be.an('object'));",
                  "if (mine) pm.collectionVariables.set('restaurantId', mine.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/restaurants", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["restaurants"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Customer (una vez)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', j.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('customerUserId', j.userId);",
                  "  pm.test('Customer registrado', () => pm.expect(j.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "} else {",
                  "  pm.test('Customer ya existía (usa Login Customer)', () => pm.expect([400,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer@test.com\",\n  \"username\": \"customer1\",\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Uno\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"tlf\": \"600333444\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Customer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', j.token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('customerUserId', j.userId);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
